text: Han Xinyun and Darija Jurak were the defending champions but both players chose not to participate. Cori Gauff and Caty McNally won the title, defeating Maria Sanchez and Fanny Stollár in the final, 6–2, 6–2. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Citi Open - Doubles Category:Washington Open (tennis)
